{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"toolu_vrtx_01WsWro9mwA55v2F8141Z99n","content":"[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"{\\\"id\\\":\\\"JEM-89\\\",\\\"title\\\":\\\"State file for thread links and workspace history\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"Add `src/state.rs` to read/write `~/.config/ishi/state.toml`. Two data structures:\\\\n\\\\n* **Thread links**: maps thread ID → issue identifier + workspace path. One issue can have many threads, but each thread belongs to exactly one issue.\\\\n* **Workspace history**: ordered list of previously used directory paths, most recent first. Used by the workspace picker when starting new threads.\\\\n\\\\nFunctions: `load()`, `save()`, `add_thread_link()`, `threads_for_issue()`, `add_workspace()`, `workspaces()`.\\\\n\\\\nUnit tests with tempfile for round-trip serialization.\\\",\\\"projectMilestone\\\":{\\\"id\\\":\\\"d2f17c9a-0039-4861-a5db-b44495d5ec6b\\\",\\\"name\\\":\\\"Phase 5: Amp Integration\\\"},\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://linear.app/squareup/issue/JEM-89\\\",\\\"gitBranchName\\\":\\\"jmawson/jem-89-state-file-for-thread-links-and-workspace-history\\\",\\\"createdAt\\\":\\\"2026-03-18T04:51:07.087Z\\\",\\\"updatedAt\\\":\\\"2026-03-18T05:25:51.517Z\\\",\\\"archivedAt\\\":null,\\\"completedAt\\\":\\\"2026-03-18T05:25:51.486Z\\\",\\\"dueDate\\\":null,\\\"slaStartedAt\\\":null,\\\"slaMediumRiskAt\\\":null,\\\"slaHighRiskAt\\\":null,\\\"slaBreachesAt\\\":null,\\\"slaType\\\":\\\"all\\\",\\\"status\\\":\\\"Done\\\",\\\"labels\\\":[],\\\"attachments\\\":[],\\\"documents\\\":[],\\\"createdBy\\\":\\\"Jeremy Mawson\\\",\\\"createdById\\\":\\\"f265a57f-26ba-4ba6-a014-a1414e9067c4\\\",\\\"assignee\\\":\\\"Jeremy Mawson\\\",\\\"assigneeId\\\":\\\"f265a57f-26ba-4ba6-a014-a1414e9067c4\\\",\\\"project\\\":\\\"ishi\\\",\\\"projectId\\\":\\\"032af957-d258-43a4-9cac-246a45582daa\\\",\\\"team\\\":\\\"Jem\\\",\\\"teamId\\\":\\\"3dddde93-b00c-4573-a596-2475a0f69d3a\\\"}\"}]","is_error":false}]},"par